content.rendered:
Automax is proud to announce that our website is up and running.

Thanks to the Team at Giant Media, we were able to work closely together and create a stylish website for all our 4WD enthusiasts. Our new website allows everyone to see who we are and what we have to offer. The website showcasing our shop and new products, along with a gallery revealing our work. Giant Media was able to make a easy way for people to search by vehicle, brand or product type the website is jam packed with everything 4X4.

 A huge shout out to Giant Media for helping us out and being able to create a fresh, easy to use website for our company.
